# Agent-operating-brief drops at repo root. PROMPT.md is a reserved daemon-generated
# runtime filename (routes_quick_actions/routes_benchmarks/tools/fast_money write it into a
# spawned session's project cwd) -- it must never be committed as source at the repo root.
/PROMPT.md
/IMPROVEMENT-BRIEF.md

